
How to run the code normally-
1. make
2. run this command for the mpi barriers- mpirun -np (num of processes) ./executable
3. run this command for the combined barrier- mpirun -np (num of processes) ./executable (num of threads)

Here num of processes and num of threads are arguments.  

How to run code on Cluster-
1. make
2. Run this command - qsub ./mpi.pbs 
3. Script will run both MPI barriers
4. Run this command - qsub ./combined.pbs
5. Script will run the combined barrier
